(137, '_transient_dash_88ae138922fe95674369b1cb3d215a2b', '<div class="rss-widget"><ul><li><a class=''rsswidget'' href=''https://wordpress.org/news/2015/12/clifford/''>WordPress 4.4 “Clifford”</a> <span class="rss-date">December 8, 2015</span><div class="rssSummary">Version 4.4 of WordPress, named “Clifford” in honor of jazz trumpeter Clifford Brown, is available for download or update in your WordPress dashboard. New features in 4.4 make your site more connected and responsive. Clifford also introduces a new default theme, Twenty Sixteen. Introducing Twenty Sixteen Our newest default theme, Twenty Sixteen, is a modern take [&hellip;]</div></li></ul></div><div class="rss-widget"><ul><li><a class=''rsswidget'' href=''http://wptavern.com/zac-gordon-to-kickstart-javascript-master-course-for-wordpress''>WPTavern: Zac Gordon to Kickstart JavaScript Master Course for WordPress</a></li><li><a class=''rsswidget'' href=''http://wptavern.com/poll-shows-majority-consider-public-redistribution-of-commercial-themes-and-plugins-to-be-unethical''>WPTavern: Poll Shows Majority Consider Public Redistribution of Commercial Themes and Plugins to be Unethical</a></li><li><a class=''rsswidget'' href=''http://wptavern.com/how-to-restore-the-get-shortlink-button-in-wordpress-4-4''>WPTavern: How to Restore the Get Shortlink Button in WordPress 4.4</a></li></ul></div><div class="rss-widget"><ul><li class=''dashboard-news-plugin''><span>Popular Plugin:</span> <a href=''https://wordpress.org/plugins/google-analytics-dashboard-for-wp/'' class=''dashboard-news-plugin-link''>Google Analytics Dashboard for WP</a>&nbsp;<span>(<a href=''plugin-install.php?tab=plugin-information&amp;plugin=google-analytics-dashboard-for-wp&amp;_wpnonce=36f604cc35&amp;TB_iframe=true&amp;width=600&amp;height=800'' class=''thickbox'' title=''Google Analytics Dashboard for WP''>Install</a>)</span></li></ul></div>', 'no'),
